<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1>Your login code</h1>
  <p>Use the following code to log in to your account:</p>
  <p style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    {{code}}
  </p>
  <p>This code expires in <strong>{{expiresMinutes}} minutes</strong>.</p>
  <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">If you did not request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
</body>
</html>
